      Hotel details
      This lively casino hotel is 1 mile from the Las Vegas Convention Center, and a 15-minute walk from shops and dining at the Fashion Show Mall. … MORE

      The straightforward rooms have Wi-Fi access and flat-screen TVs.

      Free circus shows are offered. There’s a gym and 2 seasonal outdoor pools, plus live entertainment. Other amenities include an indoor theme park, and a lively casino with slots and table games, plus shops, meeting space and multiple dining options. There's also an RV park.
